---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Westside: The 500 Cr Scale | Yatish Shirsath">
  
  <div class="fixed top-0 left-0 h-1 bg-black z-50 w-full scale-x-0 animate-[progress_1s_ease-out_forwards] origin-left"></div>

  <header class="relative min-h-[90vh] flex flex-col justify-end p-6 md:p-12 overflow-hidden bg-[#F5F5F3]">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-10 grayscale" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1483985988355-763728e1935b?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;"></div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto w-full">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between gap-8 border-b border-black pb-8 mb-8">
        <div>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-4 block text-gray-500">Case Study 01 • Westside - TATA Enterprise</span>
          <h1 class="font-['Playfair_Display'] text-5xl md:text-8xl leading-[0.9] text-black italic">
            Fashioning<br/> <span class="not-italic font-bold">Scale.</span>
          </h1>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-xs">
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed font-medium text-gray-800">
            How we unified the digital & physical experience to help Westside achieve its <span class="bg-black text-white px-1">500 Cr Revenue</span> milestone.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">
        <div>
          <span class="block text-gray-400 mb-1">Role</span>
          <span class="text-black font-bold">Design Manager</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="block text-gray-400 mb-1">Impact</span>
          <span class="text-black font-bold">Revenue Growth</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="block text-gray-400 mb-1">Focus</span>
          <span class="text-black font-bold">Omnichannel</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="block text-gray-400 mb-1">Year</span>
          <span class="text-black font-bold">2025-26</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="py-24 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start">
        <div class="md:col-span-4 md:sticky md:top-32">
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-red-600 uppercase tracking-widest block mb-4">01 • The Problem</span>
          <h2 class="font-['Playfair_Display'] text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-tight mb-6">
            The "Leaky Bucket"<br/> <span class="italic text-gray-400">Effect.</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Westside had the traffic, but the experience was fragmented. The "Phygital" gap was bleeding revenue through discovery paralysis and checkout fatigue.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-16">
          <div class="group">
            <div class="aspect-[16/9] bg-gray-100 mb-6 overflow-hidden relative">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm">[Snapshot: Old Confusing Filters]</div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-baseline border-t border-gray-200 pt-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-red-500 font-bold">A.</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-1">Discovery Paralysis</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Overwhelming grids with poor filtering logic made finding products a chore, leading to high bounce rates on listing pages.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="group">
            <div class="aspect-[16/9] bg-gray-100 mb-6 overflow-hidden relative">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm">[Snapshot: Long Checkout Form]</div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-baseline border-t border-gray-200 pt-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-red-500 font-bold">B.</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-1">Checkout Fatigue</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">A multi-step, slow checkout process on mobile was killing impulse buys. Forced logins were causing massive drop-offs.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-32 bg-[#0F0F0F] text-[#F5F5F3] relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-purple-900/20 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
      <div class="text-center mb-24">
        <span class="inline-block border border-white/20 px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-6 text-white/60">New Segment Launch</span>
        <h2 class="font-['Playfair_Display'] text-5xl md:text-7xl mb-6">Whitedoor.</h2>
        <p class="max-w-xl mx-auto text-white/60 text-lg font-light leading-relaxed">
          To hit the 500 Cr target, we needed higher AOV. We launched a bespoke digital experience for the luxury customer.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-4 transition-transform hover:-translate-y-2 duration-500">
             <div class="w-full h-full bg-black/40 flex items-center justify-center text-xs tracking-widest text-white/30">MINIMALIST UI</div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-['Playfair_Display'] text-2xl italic">Quiet Luxury</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/50 leading-relaxed">Stripped away the noise. High-end photography guidelines and generous whitespace.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 md:pt-16"> <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-4 transition-transform hover:-translate-y-2 duration-500">
             <div class="w-full h-full bg-black/40 flex items-center justify-center text-xs tracking-widest text-white/30">PREMIUM CHECKOUT</div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-['Playfair_Display'] text-2xl italic">Velvet Rope</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/50 leading-relaxed">A streamlined, "guest-first" checkout flow that feels exclusive, not bureaucratic.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-4 transition-transform hover:-translate-y-2 duration-500">
             <div class="w-full h-full bg-black/40 flex items-center justify-center text-xs tracking-widest text-white/30">EDITORIAL LAYOUT</div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-['Playfair_Display'] text-2xl italic">Storytelling</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/50 leading-relaxed">Product pages that tell the story of the fabric and the fit, increasing desire.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 px-6 bg-[#F5F5F3]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        
        <div>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-blue-600 uppercase tracking-widest block mb-4">02 • Behind the Scenes</span>
          <h2 class="font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-6 leading-tight">
            Design isn't just pixels.<br/>It's Operations.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            The biggest bottleneck was the IT skill gap. Instead of complaining, I became a partner. Managing diverse inputs from Marketing, IT, and Branding required a new playbook.
          </p>

          <ul class="space-y-6">
            <li class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 border border-black flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg flex-shrink-0 bg-white">1</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold">Weekly QC Rituals</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">Instituted mandatory weekly reviews to catch bugs before UAT, reducing hotfixes by 40%.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 border border-black flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg flex-shrink-0 bg-white">2</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold">Code as a Deliverable</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">I provided HTML/CSS snippets for complex interactions, ensuring the dev team built exactly what was designed.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 border border-black flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg flex-shrink-0 bg-white">3</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold">Automated Support</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">Launched an AI Chatbot to handle Tier-1 queries, freeing up human agents for complex issues.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="relative">
          <div class="aspect-square bg-white border border-black p-2 md:rotate-3 transition-transform hover:rotate-0">
            <div class="h-full w-full bg-gray-50 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-300 font-mono text-xs">
              [Image: Your Team / Whiteboard Session]
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-black text-white p-6 max-w-xs shadow-xl">
            <p class="font-['Playfair_Display'] italic text-xl mb-2">"Yatish bridged the gap between creative vision and engineering reality."</p>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400">— Stakeholder Feedback</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 px-6 border-t border-black">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-12 text-gray-400">Project Outcomes</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <div>
          <span class="block text-6xl md:text-8xl font-['Playfair_Display'] font-bold mb-4">500<span class="text-4xl">Cr</span></span>
          <p class="font-medium">Revenue Milestone Hit</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="block text-6xl md:text-8xl font-['Playfair_Display'] font-bold mb-4">40<span class="text-4xl">%</span></span>
          <p class="font-medium">Reduction in Support Tickets</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="block text-6xl md:text-8xl font-['Playfair_Display'] font-bold mb-4">New</span>
          <p class="font-medium">Luxury Segment Established</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="py-32 bg-black text-white text-center">
    <a href="/work/luca-faloni" class="group inline-block">
      <span class="font-mono text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 block group-hover:text-white transition-colors">Read Next Case Study</span>
      <h2 class="font-['Playfair_Display'] text-4xl md:text-6xl italic group-hover:underline decoration-1 underline-offset-8">
        Luca Faloni: <br/> The Logistics Logic
      </h2>
    </a>
  </div>

</Layout>